column5: Rm Classic cars.... Great place ! I remember driving past Robs old shop years ago ! And now to see where they are and how big they have gotten... its crazy !

Yah... if only this was one of the original dozen...  http://www.rmauctions.com/FeatureCars.cfm?...D=r082&fc=0  Went for years and years to sit and watch junk go across the block for 3 days with the odd gem.  Keep saying I should take mine down and run it across the block... but not in this economy.
That 69 Camaro should fetch 6 figures. Which is 5 figures more than I can afford right now.
Camaro........All I could see was mighty MOPARS    long live the Rapid Transit System
